467
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:18,000
Sal û a nebî bîçîm û xweş bûn, miribû...
 
Years... harvest... and were good, died...

468
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:32,000
[Unintelligible]
 
[Unintelligible]

469
