00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:42,000
Hemdila ji Xwedê re.
 
Praise be to God.

522
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:44,000
Xwedê we neke ber destan.
 
May God not leave you in need of others.

523
00:35:44,000 --> 00:35:44,000
