Yes.

554
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:57,000
Maşalla lê bigre hewşê lê bigre.
 
Mashallah record here, record the courtyard.

555
00:36:57,000 --> 00:37:13,000
Maşalla.
 
Mashallah.

556
